data.description: 4 Bed/2.5 bath. Madison City Schools. Smart Home system, downstairs and upstairs thermostats can be set from panel or smart phone. Smooth Walls & ceilings. Luxury vinyl flooring downstairs. Kitchen with large island looks into Great Room. Stainless Steel Appliances. Walk in pantry. Isolated Master Suite features walk-in closet. Master bath features double sinks, Garden tub and separate shower. Covered Front & Rear Patio. 2 Car Garage. Sprinkler system. Fenced backyard. House to be sold as is where is seller to make no repairs, no knows issues. Home does need new carpet and paint throughout. Homeowners have access to lake & Walking Trails; 4 Miles from Redstone Arsenal.
